trans-unit.source: Defines values for specifying the parts of a <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewCell"></xref> that are to be painted.
trans-unit.target: Definieert de waarden voor het opgeven van de onderdelen van een <xref href="System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewCell"> </xref> die moeten worden getekend.

trans-unit.source: This enumeration is used by the protected <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewCell.Paint%2A?displayProperty=fullName> method and by handlers for the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.CellPainting>, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.RowPrePaint>, and <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.RowPostPaint> events of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView> control.
trans-unit.target: Deze opsomming wordt gebruikt door de beveiligde <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewCell.Paint%2A?displayProperty=fullName>methode en door handlers voor de <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.CellPainting>, <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.RowPrePaint>, en <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.RowPostPaint>gebeurtenissen van de <xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView>besturingselement.</xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.RowPostPaint> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.RowPrePaint> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridView.CellPainting> </xref:System.Windows.Forms.DataGridViewCell.Paint%2A?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.target: Alle onderdelen van de cel moeten worden getekend.
